22%20Crore%20in%20Dues%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13133530%2FThe_Prime_Minister_Shri_Narendra_Modi_at_the_laying_of_foundation_stone_and_dedication_to_the_Nation_of_Multiple_Projects_worth_over_Rs._8000_crore_at_Amod_Bharuch_in_Gujarat_on_October_10_2022_2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Gujarat%20government%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2023%2Foct%2F13%2Fgujarat-unpaid-bill-for-hiring-state-buses-spirals-in-3-yrs-2623528.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520government%2520said%2520that%2520in%2Care%2520yet%2520to%2520be%2520paid.%5C%22%3Enot%20paid%3C%2Fa%3E%20more%20than%20Rs%2022%20crore%20in%20rent%20for%20public%20transport%20buses%20that%20were%20hired%20to%20ferry%20people%20to%20events%20that%20were%20attended%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20or%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Gujarat%20over%20the%20past%20three%20financial%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20numbers%20were%20revealed%20in%20response%20to%20a%20question%20raised%20by%20Congres%20MLA%20Jignesh%20Mevani%20in%20the%20Gujarat%20assembly.%20The%20data%20also%20showed%20that%20while%20only%20122%20buses%20were%20used%20in%202020-21%20to%20bring%20people%20to%20government%20programmes%20that%20Modi%20or%20the%20Gujarat%20chief%20minister%20attended%2C%20this%20ballooned%20to%2031%2C211%20in%202022-23.%20In%202020-21%2C%20fewer%20events%20would%20have%20been%20held%20due%20to%20the%20COVID-19%20lockdowns%20and%20subsequent%20restrictions%20on%20physical%20gatherings.%20Vijay%20Rupani%20and%20Bhupendra%20Patel%20have%20been%20chief%20ministers%20of%20Gujarat%20during%20that%20three-year%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Gujarat%20State%20Road%20Transport%20Corporation%20(GSRTC)%20said%20that%20a%20total%20of%2034%2C868%20buses%20were%20allocated%20for%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20Chief%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20events%20in%20the%