ant%20for%20transporting%20rural%20people%2C%20not%20to%20gather%20crowds%20for%20government%20events.%20The%20rural%20transport%20is%20hit%20when%20the%20government%20hires%20ST%20buses%20on%20a%20big%20scale%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697188527000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13133530%2FThe_Prime_Minister_Shri_Narendra_Modi_at_the_laying_of_foundation_stone_and_dedication_to_the_Nation_of_Multiple_Projects_worth_over_Rs._8000_crore_at_Amod_Bharuch_in_Gujarat_on_October_10_2022_2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fgujarat-government-public-transport-buses-rent-dues-pm-cm%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20transport%20department%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cproceedings%20for%20the%20recovery%20of%20dues%20are%20in%20progress%20with%20the%20departments%20concerned.%E2%80%9D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fgujarat-government-public-transport-buses-rent-dues-pm-cm%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Some%20Walmart%20employees%20say%20customers%20are%20getting%20hostile%20at%20self-checkout%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they%20blame%20anti-theft%20tech%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Collage%20featuring%20Walmart%20employees%2C%20and%20a%20dome%20security%20surveillance%20system%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f8da378a784000196197a9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIf%20the%20missed-scan%20detection%20technology%20detects%20a%20problem%20a%20light%20above%20the%20machine%20illuminates%2C%20and%20it%20sends%20a%20text%20notification%20to%20a%20handheld%20device%20for%20employees%20assigned%20to%20the%20area.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3B%20Shutterstock%3B%20Alyssa%20Powell%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigur