C2%A0unbreakable%20bond%20between%20me%20and%20my%20sons.%20My%20American%20friends%20envied%20the%20quality%20time%20I%C2%A0spent%20with%20my%20little%20ones%20during%20their%20most%20formative%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20two%20vastly%20different%20experiences%20shed%20light%20on%20the%20different%20values%20that%20these%20locations%20place%20on%20children%20and%20the%20family%20unit%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20those%20of%20us%20in%20the%20US%20can%20still%20do%20a%20better%20job%20of%20supporting%20families%20%E2%80%94%20and%20particularly%20making%20maternity%20leave%20more%20accessible.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20experienced%20surprising%20differences%20when%20relocating%20and%20would%20like%20to%20share%20your%20story%2C%20please%20contact%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fjenna-gyimesi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EJenna%20Gyimesi%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3Eat%20jgyimesi%40Insider.com.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmaternity-leave-in-europe-vs-us-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697188082000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652069136e038039826c588c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmaternity-leave-in-europe-vs-us-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Maternity%20leave%20in%20Europe%20was%20eye%20opening%20for%20a%20working%20mom%20who%20didn't%20feel%20supported%20or%20get%20any%20time%20off%20after%20her%20first%20son's%20birth%20in%20the%20US.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Robin%20Madell)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmaternity-leave-in-europe-vs-us-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Saudi%20Arabia%E2%80%99s%20Neom%20Hub%20Teams%20With%20Korean%20Fil