%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Uttar%20Pradesh%3A%20Retired%20IPS%20Officer%20S.R.%20Darapuri%20Among%206%20Held%20for%20Protest%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13131516%2FScreenshot-2023-10-13-at-1.15.02%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Retired%20Indian%20Police%20Services%20officer%20S.R.%20Darapuri%20is%20among%20six%20activists%20who%20were%20arrested%20on%20October%2011%20for%20protesting%20at%20a%20Commissioner%E2%80%99s%20officer%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Gorakhpur%20district%20with%20the%20demand%20that%20Dalit%20families%20in%20the%20state%20get%20an%20acre%20of%20land%20each%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Flucknow%2Factivist-darapuri-french-national-among-seven-held-8980616%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDarapuri%2C%20a%20noted%20critic%20of%20the%20government%20and%20an%20activist%2C%20is%2079%20years%20old.%20It%20is%20unclear%20if%20he%20and%20the%20others%20who%20were%20held%20have%20been%20released%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPolice%20claimed%20that%20the%20protest%20on%20October%2010%20was%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20Section%20144%20of%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%20in%20place%20there%20at%20the%20time.%20Police%20have%20claimed%20the%20protesters%20engaged%20in%20vandalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20came%20yesterday%20to%20attend%20the%20public%20meeting%20organised%20by%20the%20Gorakhpur%20Ambedkar%20Jan%20Morcha%20regarding%20issues%20of%20Dalit%20communities%20and%20civil%20rights%20and%20the%20meeting%20was%20concluded%20peacefully.%20This%20morning%20Gorakhpur%20police%20came%20to%20take%20me%20to%20the%20police%20station%2C%E2%80%9D%20Darapuri%20wrote%20on%20Facebook%20on%20October%2011.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20others%20include%20a%20French%20national%2C%20one%20Valentine%20Jean%2C