0In%20Casualties%2C%20Harm%20Israel%20Too%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20mass%20movement%20of%20people%20fleeing%20from%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza%20will%20lead%20to%20devastating%20humanitarian%20consequences%2C%20the%20United%20Nations%20has%20warned%20after%20Israel%20forces%20asked%20Gaza%20city%20residents%20to%20move%20south.%20Israel%20described%20as%20shameful%20the%20UN's%20response%20to%20the%20warning%2C%20which%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20an%20indication%20of%20Tel%20Aviv's%20plan%20to%20launch%20a%20ground%20offensive%20in%20Gaza%20in%20retaliation%20to%20the%20Hamas%20attacks%20last%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIsrael's%20Ground%20Offensive%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAbout%20a%20couple%20of%20hours%20back%2C%20the%20official%20handle%20of%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20put%20out%20a%20post%20on%20X.%20The%20post%20asked%20Gaza%20city%20residents%20to%20evacuate%20their%20homes%20and%20move%20south%20for%20their%20safety.%20The%20post%20says%20the%20residents%20should%20return%20to%20Gaza%20city%20only%20after%20Israel's%20notification.%20It%20also%20asked%20them%20not%20to%20approach%20the%20fence%20separating%20Gaza%20from%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIDF%20announcement%20sent%20to%20civilians%20of%20Gaza%20City%3A%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20The%20IDF%20calls%20for%20the%20evacuation%20of%20all%20civilians%20of%20Gaza%20City%20from%20their%20homes%20southwards%20for%20their%20own%20safety%20and%20protection%20and%20move%20to%20the%20area%20south%20of%20the%20Wadi%20Gaza%2C%20as%20shown%20on%20the%20map.%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20The%20Hamas%20terrorist%20organization%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20(%40IDF)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIDF%2Fstatus%2F1712707301369434398%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2013%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHamas%20terrorists%20are%20hiding%20in%20Gaza%20City%20in%20tunnels%20under%20houses%20in%20Gaza%20City%2C%20and%20inside%20many%20buildings%20are%20innocent%20civilians.%20The%20IDF%20will%20continue%20to%20operate%20significantly%20in%20Gaza%20City%20in%20the%20coming%20days%2C%20and%20wishes%20to%20avoid%20harming%20civilians%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20post%20read.%20Earlier%2C%20news%20agency%20Reuters%20had%20reported%20that%20Israel%20Defence%20Minister%20Yoav%20Gallant%20had%20told%20soldiers%20about%20a%20ground%20offensive%20plan.%20%26quot%3BHamas%20wanted%20a%20change%20and%20it%20will%20get%20one.%20What%20was%20in%20Gaza%20will%20no%20longer%20be.%20We%20started%20the%20offensive%20from%20the%20air%2C%20later%20on%20we%20will%20also%20come%20from%20the%20ground%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUN's%20Warning%2C%20Israel's%20Response%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUN%20spokesperson%20Stephane%20Dujarric%20said%20the%20population%20that%20Israel%20wants%20to%20move%20to%20the%20south%20of%20Gaza%20is%20approximately%201.1%20million%20people.%20The%20UN%20%26quot%3Bconsiders%20it%20impossible%20for%20such%20a%20movement%20to%20take%20place%20without%20devastating%20humanitarian%20consequences%26quot%3B%2C%20Dujarric%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20drew%20a%20sharp%20response%20from%20Gilad%20Erdan%2C%20Israel's%20ambassador%20to%20the%20UN.%20%26quot%3BFor%20years%20now%2C%20the%20UN%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bturning%20a%20blind%20eye%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20arming%20of%20Hamas%20and%20its%20use%20of%20civilians%20to%20hide%20its%20murderous%20instruments.%20And%20now%2C%20instead%20of%20standing%20by%20Israel%20after%20the%20massacre%20by%20Hamas%2C%20they%20dare%20to%20preach%20to%20us%20when%20Israel%20tries%20to%20minimise%20harm%20to%20civilians.%20Right%20now%2C%20the%20only%20thing%20the%20UN%20should%20focus%20on%20is%20the%20return%20of%20the%20abductees%20to%20Israel.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENews%20agency%20Reuters%20has%20reported%20that%20a%20Hamas%20spokesperson%20has%20asked%20Gaza%20citizens%20not%20to%20heed%20Israel's%20warnings.%20Salama%20Marouf%20has%20said%20the%20relocation%20warning%20was%20Israel's%20attempt%20%26quot%3Bto%20broadcast%20and%20pass%20on%20fake%20propaganda%2C%20aiming%20to%20sow%20confusion%20among%20citizens%20and%20harm%20our%20internal%20cohesion%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Is%20Gaza's%20Situation%20Now%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGaza%20is%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20running%20out%20of%20critical%20supplies%2C%20the%20UN%20has%20warned.%20More%20than%203%20lakh%20people%20have%20been%20displaced%20by%20Israel's%20air%20strikes.%20More%20than%20two-thirds%20of%20them%20have%20taken%20shelter%20in%20schools%20run%20by%20the%20UN.%20Over%202%2C500%20homes%20have%20been%20destroyed%20or%20are%20uninhabitable%20now%2C%20a%20UN%20report%20has%20said.%20At%20least%2088%20education%20facilities%20have%20been%20struck.%20UN's%20rights%20experts%20have%20called%20upon%20Hamas%20to%20release%20hostages%20it%20took%20during%20its%20attack%20on%20Israel.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20they%20have%20said%20there%20is%20no%20justification%20for%20Israel's%20%26quot%3Bindiscriminate%20attacks%26quot%3B%20on%20Palestinian%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fv727atfg_israel-_625x300_13_October_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20report%20warned%20that%20water%20crisis%20is%20worsening%20across%20Gaza%20Strip%20due%20to%20damaged%20infrastructure%20and%20lack%20of%20electricity%20due%20to%20Israel%20siege.%20%26quot%3BWater%20supplies%20cannot%20be%20replenished%20due%20to%20the%20total%20blockade%20on%20the%20Strip%20by%20the%20Israelis%20authorities.%20Fuel%20cannot%20be%20brought%20in%2C%20and%20Israeli%20water%20suppliers%20can%20no%20longer%20deliver%20water%20in%20Gaza%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20UN's%20sexual%20and%20reproductive%20health%20agency%20said%20Gaza%20currently%20has%2050%2C000%20pregnant%20women%2C%20who%20cannot%20access%20health%20services.%20About%205%2C500%20of%20them%20are%20due%20to%20give%20birth%20in%20the%20next%20month.%20According%20to%20a%20UN%20report%20published%20yesterday%2C%201%2C000%20people%2C%20including%20over%20300%20children%2C%20have%20died%20since%20the%20October%207%20attacks%20sparked%20a%20wave%20of%20violence.%20Twelve%20UN%20staff%20members%20have%20also%20lost%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPossible%20Impacts%20Of%20Ground%20Offensive%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20mass%20movement%20of%20over%20a%20million%20people%2C%20many%20of%20them%20women%20and%20children%2C%20in%20a%20war%20zone%20is%20likely%20to%20lead%20to%20very%20high%20casualties.%20It%20will%20also%20hit%20already-disrupted%20supply%20for%20food%20and%20medicines.%20The%20ground%20offensive%20may%20also%20prompt%20Hezbollah%20to%20scale%20up%20their%20involvement%20in%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war.%20Israel%20and%20Hezbollah%20have%20been%20exchanging%20fire%20along%20the%20Lebanon%20border%20but%20there%20has%20not%20been%20an%20all-out%20confrontation%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fsku7ntno_israel-_625x300_13_October_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EHezbollah%20and%20Hamas%20have%20long%20been%20part%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bjoint%20operations%20room%26quot%3B%20that%20includes%20Quds%20Force%20--%20the%20foreign%20operations%20arm%20of%20Iran's%20Islamic%20Revolutionary%20Guard%20Corps%20--%20a%20source%20close%20to%20the%20Hezbollah%20told%20AFP.%20The%20groups%20are%20part%20of%20the%20so-called%20%26quot%3Baxis%20of%20resistance%26quot%3B%20--%20Lebanese%2C%20Palestinian%2C%20Syrian%20and%20other%20Iran-backed%20armed%20opposition%20to%20Israel.%20%26quot%3BA%20decisive%20attack%20against%20one%20of%20the%20components%20of%20this%20alliance%26quot%3B%20would%20prompt%20%26quot%3Bthe%20intervention%20of%20other%20components%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20Mohanad%20Hage%20Ali%20from%20the%20Carnegie%20Middle%20East%20Center.%20%26quot%3BHezbollah%20could%20find%20itself%20forced%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20war%26quot%3B%20if%20a%20ground%20offensive%20begins%2C%20the%20analyst%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Cost%20For%20Israel%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20Israel%2C%20carrying%20out%20a%20ground%20offensive%20in%20Gaza%20and%20wiping%20out%20Hamas%20is%20a%20task%20easier%20said%20than%20done.%20Giora%20Eiland%2C%20former%20head%20of%20Israel's%20National%20Security%20Council%2C%20told%20Reuters%20earlier%20this%20week%20that%20airstrikes%20in%20Gaza%20%26quot%3Bseemed%20very%20similar%20to%20previous%20Israeli%20operations%26quot%3B%20but%20these%20tactics%20had%20not%20neutralised%20Hamas.%20The%20Israel%20government%2C%20he%20said%20then%2C%20was%20reluctant%20to%20start%20a%20ground%20initiative%20because%20it%20%26quot%3Bmight%20involve%20many%2C%20many%20more%20Israeli%20casualties%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fbql8n2oo_israel-map_625x300_13_October_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20ground%20offensive%2C%20Israel%20would%20lose%20its%20edge%20in%20firepower%20as%20it%20takes%20on%20a%20group%20well-acquainted%20with%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%20Hamas%20has%20been%20controlling%20Gaza%20for%2017%20years%20now%20and%20during%20this%20time%20it%20has%20built%20a%20network%20of%20tunnels%20its%20operatives%20can%20att