20slumping%2C%20etc.%20and%20run%20the%20risk%20of%20causing%20GLOFs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPossible%20drivers%20of%20the%20flood%20from%20the%20South%20Lhonak%20Lake%20on%20the%20night%20of%20October%203%2C%202023%2C%20have%20been%20a%20debated%20topic.%20It%20started%20with%20the%20cloudburst%20theory%20as%20early%20as%206%3A00%20am%20on%20October%204.%20By%20the%20evening%20of%20October%204%2C%20the%20day%20of%20the%20flash%20floods%2C%20an%20alternative%20narrative%20had%20set%20in%2C%20questioning%20the%20cloudburst%20theory.%20There%20were%20apprehensions%20like%20whether%20cloudbursts%20occur%20in%20the%20Trans-Himalayan%20region%20and%20that%20the%20lake%20area%20under%20debate%20typically%20receives%20minimal%20rainfall%20according%20to%20historical%20records%20or%20that%20the%20occurrence%20of%20cloudbursts%20in%20such%20a%20high-altitude%20area%20is%20somewhat%20surprising.%20There%20was%20no%20clear-cut%20answer.%20Nevertheless%2C%20many%20people%20were%20hinting%20towards%20the%20recent%20Nepal%20earthquake%20and%20the%20possibility%20of%20it%20triggering%20the%20lake%20burst.%20Now%2C%20with%20deeper%20analysis%2C%20geoscientists%20are%20increasingly%20believing%20that%20the%20collapse%20of%20a%20lateral%20moraine%20%5Bdebris%20such%20as%20soil%20and%20rock%20left%20behind%20by%20the%20edge%20of%20a%20melting%20glacier%5D%20leading%20to%20a%20landslide%20into%20the%20lake%20is%20the%20likely%20cause%20of%20the%20GLOF.%20Anything%20could%20be%20possible%3A%20cloudburst%2C%20the%20Nepal%20earthquake%20or%20other%20geomorphic%20processes.%20It%20will%20take%20time%20for%20the%20experts%20to%20ascertain%20what%20exactly%20led%20to%20the%20sizable%20floating%20ice%20to%20occupy%20the%20lake%20area%2C%20forcing%20the%20lake%20water%20to%20find%20its%20way%20downwards%20and%20take%20the%20form%20of%20a%20GLOF.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13122637%2FIG-POST720.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13122637%2FIG-POST720.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13122637%2FIG-POST720-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13122637%2FIG-POST720-1024x1024.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13122637%2FIG-POST720-150x150.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-679891%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPhoto%3A%20International%20Rivers%2C%20CC%20BY%20NC%20SA%202.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20you%20think%20that%20both%20climate%20change%20and%20human%20activities%20%E2%80%94%20specifically%2C%20the%20construction%20of%20not%20just%20the%20Teesta-III%20but%20all%20five%20other%20dams%20on%20the%20river%20%E2%80%94%20are%20to%20blame%C2%A0here%3F%20There%20are%20also%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fas-sikkim-picks-up-pieces-teesta-iii-reservoir-opening-of-its-gates-under-lens-8974047%2F%5C%22%3Etalks%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0of%20the%20spillways%20not%20being%20opened%20in%20time%2C%20which%20could%20have%20at%20least%20decreased%20the%20impact%20to%20some%20extent%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EClimate%20change%20has%20been%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20debate%20for%20the%20changing%20Himalayan%20geo-environment.%20Scientists%20are%20repeatedly%20warning%20that%20the%20Himalaya%20are%20warming%20comparatively%20faster%20than%20their%20lowland%20counterparts.%20The%20rapidly%20warming%20Himalaya%20has%20led%20to%20an%20acceleration%20of%20various%20geomorphic%20processes%2C%20including%20melting%20of%20glaciers.%20The%20rapid%20melting%20of%20glaciers%20has%20further%20given%20rise%20to%20many%20potentially%20dangerous%20Glacial%20Lakes%2C%20in%20recent%20times.%20The%20changes%20in%20the%20geomorphic%20processes%20have%20been%20rapid%20and%20dam%20planners%2Fengineers%20were%20unable%20to%20foresee%20their%20increasing%20intensity%20and%20frequency%20over%2020%20years%20ago%20when%20many%20of%20our%20dams%20in%20Sikkim%20were%20planned.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20an%20officer%20of%20Teesta-III%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E42%20years%20of%20water%20data%20is%20needed%20for%20mega%20projects%20to%20be%20designed%20and%20recommended%20by%20National%20Seismic%20Designing%20Authority%20for%20the%20final%20approval%20of%20CEA%20(Central%20Electricity%20Authority).%20In%20the%20context%20of%20Teesta%20III%2C%20%5Bthe%5D%20highest%20flood%20measuring%20680%20cumecs%20(discharge)%20was%20recorded%20in%201973%20in%20Chungthang.%20Based%20on%20the%20data%20the%20Teesta%20III%20dam%20was%20designed%20to%20withhold%207000%20cumecs%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20important%20to%20understand%20that%20the%20Sikkim-Darjeeling%20Himalaya%20being%20a%20backward%20and%20less-researched%20region%20did%20not%20have%20such%20long-term%20data%20on%20the%20table%20when%20dams%20were%20planned%20and%20designed%20in%20the%20early%202000s.%20That%20is%20the%20reason%20why%20anti-dam%20activists%20often%20question%20the%20technical%2C%20environmental%20and%20human%20procedures%20followed%20by%20the%20proponents%20of%20hydropower%20dams%20in%20the%20Himalayan%20region%20including%20in%20Sikkim.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20regard%20to%20the%20reported%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Espillways%20not%20being%20opened%20on%20time%2C%20had%20the%20dam%20gates%20of%20Teesta-III%20been%20opened%20on%20time%2C%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20flood%20would%20have%20been%20much%20milder.%20However%2C%20by%20the%20time%20information%20was%20received%20by%20relevant%20people%20in%20Chungthang%2C%20the%20flood%20had%20already%20hit%20the%20dam%20forcing%20them%20to%20flee%20for%20their%20lives%2C%20instead%20of%20opening%20the%20gates.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMore%20worrying%20is%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fraju.basnet.7583%2Fposts%2Fpfbid0ACwp4raLxRjhGaP8JuQHmKvZAhrMcBdhb6cSDqvPpWz5xq5LreSNEADHTB7JWa2al%3Fmibextid%3DYxdKMJ%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estatement%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20a%20senior%20civil%20servant%20of%20the%20Govt%20of%20Sikkim%20on%20his%20Facebook%20page%20on%2007.10.23.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20487px)%2085vw%2C%20487px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13122304%2Fimage1.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22487%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13122304%2Fimage1.png%20487w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13122304%2Fimage1-300x233.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-679888%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22378%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20above%20statement%20is%20worth%20noting.%20It%20talks%20about%20how%20the%20failure%20of%20both%20human%20coordination%20and%20an%20Early%20Warning%20System%20(EWS)%20has%20worked%20in%20tandem%2C%20giving%20us%20such%20a%20big-scale%20disaster%20that%20ravaged%20a%20major%20part%20of%20the%20Upper%20Tista%20Basin.%20The%20statement%20calls%20for%20a%20serious%20investigation%20of%20the%20entire%20fiasco.%20We%20need%20to%20bring%20the%20people%20and%20machinery%20responsible%20for%20the%20purpose%20to%20book%20for%20the%20crime%20against%20humanity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20cannot%20even%20imagine%20what%20would%20have%20happened%20to%20our%20people%20downstream%20if%20Teesta-V%20had%20not%20withstood%20the%20Tista%20flood%20and%20broken%20down%20instead.%20The%20combined%20water%20of%20two%20dams%20and%20the%20GLOF%20would%20have%20destroyed%20two%20more%20dams%20downstream%20(TDLP-III%20and%20IV)%20in%20the%20Darjeeling%20hills%20(Gorkhaland%20Territorial%20Administration)%20of%20West%20Bengal%20inflicting%20incalculable%20human%20tragedy%20and%20giving%20us%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20human%20disasters%20in%20the%20history%20of%20Eastern%20Himalaya.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnder%20such%20a%20situation%2C%20the%20Tista%E2%80%99s%20water%20would%20have%20taken%20with%20it%20most%20of%20the%20human%20settlements%20downstream%20of%20Dikchu.%20It%20would%20have%20pushed%20Sevoke%20forest%2C%20a%20small%20stretch%20that%20separates%20the%20Tista%20and%20Mahananda%20Rivers%2C%20and%20joined%20the%20Mahananda%2C%20washing%20away%20a%20major%20part%20of%20Siliguri%20City.%20Historically%2C%20the%20Tista%20joined%20the%20Mahananda%20River%20instead%20of%20the%20Brahmaputra.%20It%20was%20only%20around%201%2C787%20that%20the%20Tista%20changed%20its%20course%20and%20became%20a%20tributary%20of%20the%20Brahmaputra.%20The%20geomorphic%20history%20of%20the%20river%20is%20complex%20and%20this%20human%20failure%20in%20its%20upper%20catchment%20invites%20a%20detailed%20examination%20and%20investigations.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13123028%2FIG-POST723.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13123028%2FIG-POST723.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13123028%2FIG-POST723-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13123028%2FIG-POST723-1024x1024.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13123028%2FIG-POST723-150x150.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-679898%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPhoto%3A%20Abir1907%2FWikimedia%20Commons%2C%20CC%20BY-SA%204.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20breaching%20of%20the%20Teesta-III%20dam%20at%20Chungthang%20and%20the%20damages%20this%20has%20caused%20brings%20the%20focus%20on%20the%20numerous%20hydropower%20projects%20in%20construction%20and%20being%20planned%20in%20the%20state.%20Do%20you%20think%20poor%20dam%20construction%20is%20an%20issue%2C%20as%20Sikkim%E2%80%99s%20CM%20mentioned%3F%20More%20dams%20are%20in%20the%20works%20in%20the%20Northeast%20and%20the%20eastern%20Himalaya%20including%20Sikkim%20%E2%80%93%20such%20as%20the%20upcoming%20Dibang%20project%20in%20Arunachal%20Pradesh.%20How%20can%20we%20have%20sufficient%20checks%20in%20place%20so%20that%20threats%20such%20as%20GLOFs%20and%20others%20are%20not%20ignored%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EScientists%2C%20researchers%2C%20activists%20and%20journalists%20have%20been%20warning%20about%20the%20unplanned%20and%20haphazard%20hydro%20development%20in%20Sikkim-Darjeeling%20hills%20for%20over%20two%20decades.%20The%20central%20government%2C%20state%20government%20and%20dam%20development%20proponents%20have%2C%20however%2C%20dismissed%20the%20concerns%20as%20fear-mongering.%20They%20do%20not%20take%20researchers%20and%20research%20papers%20seriously.%20Science%20and%20policy%20hardly%20work%20in%20coordination%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20also%20interesting%20to%20note%20that%20the%20first%20Human%20Development%20Report%20(HDR)%20of%20Sikkim%20(2001)%20advises%20the%20state%20to%20harness%20the%20rich%20water%20resources%20of%20the%20Sikkim%20Himalaya.%20The%20report%20further%20recommends%20the%20state%20government%20take%20the%20help%20of%20the%20private%20sector%20towards%20this%20end%20(page%2077-84).%20Strangely%2C%20the%20same%20report%20also%20talks%20about%20glacier%20retreat%20and%20glacial%20lake%20outburst%20floods.%20The%20State%20Development%20Report%20of%20Sikkim%20(2008)%2C%20takes%20a%20similar%20stand%20as%20taken%20by%20the%202001%20HDR%20(page%20109-119).%20Both%20reports%20cite%20the%20success%20of%20the%20Chukha%20Project%20of%20Bhutan%20as%20an%20example%20for%20the%20development%20of%20hydro%20resources%20in%20Sikkim.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Sikkim%20CM%E2%80%99s%20reference%20to%20the%20poor%20construction%20of%20the%20Teesta-III%20dam%20is%20a%20little%20far-fetched%20as%20any%20mega%20development%20project%20goes%20through%20rigorous%20approval%20processes%20across%20various%20statutory%20bodies%20before%20construction%20actually%20begins.%20It%20seems%20to%20me%20more%20of%20a%20political%20statement%20as%20it%20is%20not%20backed%20by%20data%20and%20science.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscience.thewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fsikkim-flood-another-warning-greater-disaster-risk-himalayan-states%2F%5C%22%3ESikkim%20Flood%20Was%20a%20Disaster%20Forecast%20%E2%80%93%20But%20Warnings%20Were%20Ignored%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20dams%2C%20including%20the%20Teesta-III%2C%20are%20definitely%20ill-planned%20without%20properly%20internalising%20the%20Himalayan%20specificities%20and%20foreseeing%20the%20uncertainties.%20The%20consequence%20of%20ill-planned%20hydro%20ventures%20is%20before%20us%20now.%20I%20hope%20we%20shall%20take%20lessons%20from%20this%20largely%20human-made%20disaster%20and%20move%20ahead%20with%20caution%20taking%20into%20account%20the%20geologic%20and%20geomorphic%20specificities%20of%20the%20region.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20now%20a%20common%20voice%20in%20the%20region%20%E2%80%93%20no%20more%20dams.%20The%20voice%20is%20further%20strengthened%20by%20the%20statement%20of%20Karma%20Loday%20Bhutia%2C%20Sikkim%E2%80%99s%20forest%20and%20environment%20minister%2C%20opposing%20a%20dam%20in%20Chungthang%20following%20the%20Tista%20disaster.%20Sikkim%20should%20now%20concentrate%20on%20the%20efficient%20handling%20of%20the%20already%20constructed%20and%20commissioned%20hydropower%20projects%20instead%20of%20venturing%20into%20new%20ones.%20There%20should%20be%20proper%20human%20coordination%20and%20an%20EWS%20in%20place%20to%20manage%20its%20functional%20dams.%20The%20inefficiency%20and%20lack%20of%20human%20coordination%20to%20handle%20the%20current%20flash%20flood%20in%20the%20upper%20Tista%20catchment%20has%20badly%20exposed%20Sikkim.%20A%20small%20mistake%20upstream%20shall%20have%20tremendous%20human%20and%20environmental%20impacts%20downstream%20as%20it%20is%20a%20common%20river%20basin%20that%20we%20share%20in%20the%20Darjeeling%20hills%2C%20North%20Bengal%20plains%20and%20parts%20of%20northwest%20Bangladesh.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13123006%2FIG-POST722.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13123006%2FIG-POST722.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13123006%2FIG-POST722-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13123006%2FIG-POST722-1024x1024.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13123006%2FIG-POST722-150x150.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-679895%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPhoto%3A%20Pinakpani%2FWikimedia%20Commons%2C%20CC%20BY-SA%204.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Sikkim%20Himalaya%20is%20a%20geologically%20fragile%20and%20vulnerable%20system.%20What%20are%20the%20important%20steps%20that%20need%20to%20be%20taken%20to%20ensure%20that%20another%20Teesta-III%20does%20not%20happen%20in%20the%20future%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20entire%20Himalaya%20is%20a%20fragile%20resource%20zone.%20It%20is%20not%20as%20strong%20as%20it%20appears%20to%20be.%20Dynamics%20of%20change%20in%20the%20region%20are%20inextricably%20intertwined%20with%20factors%20such%20as%20climate%2C%20geology%2C%20fauna%2C%20flora%2C%20water%20resources%20etc.%20The%20region%20experiences%20various%20types%20of%20geo-environmental%2Fgeomorphic%20processes%20and%2C%20thereby%2C%20is%20prone%20to%20a%20number%20of%20natural%20hazards.%20Often%20these%20hazards%20assume%20the%20form%20of%20disaster%20due%20to%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20inherent%20nature%2C%20climatic%20conditions%20and%20lack%20of%20adequate%20disaster%20preparedness%20mechanisms%20consequently%20inflicting%20widespread%20catastrophe%20and%20human%20insecurities.%20However%2C%20more%20recently%2C%20many%20of%20the%20natural%20processes%20have%20been%20accelerated%20by%20unscientific%20and%20unsustainable%20anthropogenic%20activities%20including%20the%20construction%20of%20mega%20hydropower%20dams%20among%20others.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20state%20of%20Sikkim%2C%20with%20one%20of%20the%20highest%20densities%20of%20hydropower%20projects%20in%20the%20country%2C%20needs%20to%20evolve%20a%20comprehensive%20regional%20hydropower%20policy%20in%20view%20of%20its%20unique%20regional%20environment%2C%20ecological%20setup%20and%20geography.%20We%20need%20to%20have%20a%20sound%20hydropower%20policy%2C%20adequately%20taking%20into%20account%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20geological%20and%20geomorphic%20specificities.%20The%20mainstreaming%20of%20Disaster%20Risk%20Reduction%20(DRR)%20and%20climate%20change%20with%20hydropower%20policy%20needs%20to%20be%20prioritised.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20contingency%20plan%20for%20disaster%20management%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20disaster%20for%20all%20existing%20hydro-projects%20in%20the%20area%20is%20crucial.%20The%20Government%20of%20Sikkim%20has%20consistently%20insisted%20that%20hydropower%20projects%20are%20harmless.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELastly%2C%20the%20mainstreaming%20of%20an%20Environmental%20Management%20Plan%20(EMP)%2C%20Disaster%20Risk%20Reduction%20(DRR)%20and%20climate%20change%20in%20the%20development%20processes%20and%20projects%2C%20particularly%20in%20sensitive%20sectors%20like%20hydropower%20projects%2C%20is%20indispensable%20for%20the%20sustainable%20development%20of%20the%20region.%20This%20becomes%20important%20in%20view%20of%20the%20geo-environmental%20fragility%20and%20socio-cultural%20vulnerability%20of%20the%20Himalayan%20landscape.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fsikkim-glacial-lake-outburst-flood-impact-ecology%5C%22%3EAs%20Sikkim%20Reels%20From%20Disastrous%20Floods%2C%20Concerns%20Over%20Warning%20Signs%20and%20Enormous%20Impact%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20breaching%20of%20the%20dam%20due%20to%20a%20GLOF%20event%20was%20predicted%20by%20several%20reports%20and%20studies%3B%20in%20fact%2C%20a%20newspaper%20reportedly%20spoke%20of%20this%20possibility%20on%20September%2023.%20Is%20there%20a%20way%20that%20such%20warnings%20can%20be%20heeded%20in%20future%3F%20What%20about%20early%20warning%20systems%2C%20do%20we%20have%20any%20in%20place%20at%20all%3F%20They%20seem%20to%20be%20even%20more%20crucial%20now%20than%20ever%20before.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20no%20way%20until%20dam%20proponents%20and%20the%20government%20take%20the%20science%20and%20scientific%20findings%20seriously%3B%20%E2%80%98take%20research%20findings%20seriously%20and%20follow%20scientific%20recommendations%20religiously%E2%80%99%20is%20the%20only%20mantra.%20Politics%20and%20economics%20on%20dams%20without%20adequate%20precaution%20will%20only%20take%20us%20to%20disaster.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20have%20been%20talking%20about%20an%20early%20warning%20system%20as%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20instruments%20of%20DRR.%20That%20is%20what%20the%20Sendai%20Framework%20(2015-30)%20also%20emphasises.%20However%2C%20we%20do%20not%20have%20them%20in%20many%20critical%20hazard-prone%20areas%20like%20Potentially%20Dangerous%20Glacial%20Lakes.%20Failure%20to%20install%20an%20early%20warning%20system%20on%20time%20was%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20why%20the%20South%20Lhonak%20Lake%20outburst%20turned%20into%20a%20disaster.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Tista%20has%20calmed%20down%20now.%20She%20has%20reclaimed%20her%20lost%20spaces%20across%20much%20of%20the%20upper%20basin.%20She%20did%20not%20chase%20people%20and%20their%20property%20to%20destroy%20them.%20The%20Tista%20has%20only%20cleared%20her%20path%20for%20her%20smooth%20flow.%20She%20was%20only%20clearing%20her%20river%20bed%20badly%20encroached%20upon%20by%20human%20beings.%20This%20was%20what%20she%20had%20done%20in%201968%20and%20probably%20will%20do%20again%20in%20future%20if%20we%20do%20not%20stay%20clear%20of%20her%20path.%20Hopefully%2C%20we%20shall%20respect%20the%20space%20and%20path%20of%20the%20Tista%2C%20henceforth.%20She%20%5BTista%20is%20a%20female%2C%20Rangeet%20(a%20river%20in%20West%20Sikkim)%20is%20male%3B%20mythologically%20they%20are%20lovers%5D%20just%20needs%20respect.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13123018%2FIG-POST719.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13123018%2FIG-POST719.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13123018%2FIG-POST719-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13123018%2FIG-POST719-1024x1024.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13123018%2FIG-POST719-150x150.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-679897%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPhoto%3A%20ISRO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERebuilding%20is%20a%20tough%20task%2C%20but%20what%20are%20the%20main%20aspects%20that%20the%20state%20and%20centre%20would%20need%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%20for%20this%3F%20Local%20communities%20bear%20the%20most%20risk%20and%20many%20have%20been%20up%20in%20arms%20about%20the%20building%20of%20such%20large%20and%20small%20dams%20in%20this%20fragile%20ecosystem.%20How%20can%20administrations%20involve%20locals%E2%80%99%20concerns%20in%20the%20location%20and%20implementation%20of%20such%20infrastructure%20projects%20at%20a%20time%20when%20we%E2%80%99ve%20seen%20a%20dilution%20in%20laws%20that%20can%20protect%20local%20people%2C%20forests%20and%20such%20landscapes%20from%20such%20activities%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20a%20need%20for%20a%20sound%20and%20comprehensive%20hydro%20policy%20both%20in%20the%20Union%20and%20state%20governments%20that%20takes%20care%20of%20the%20regional%20specificities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERebuilding%20is%20a%20difficult%20task%20if%20not%20impossible.%20We%20need%20to%20have%20clear%20short-%2C%20medium-%20and%20long-term%20plans%20for%20sustainable%20reconstruction%20and%20rehabilitation.%20This%20demands%20a%20multidisciplinary%20app