p%3EHaniyeh%20is%20said%20to%20maintain%20good%20relations%20with%20the%20heads%20of%20the%20various%20Palestinian%20factions%2C%20including%20rival%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20youth%2C%20the%20Hamas%20leader%2C%20who%20is%20known%20for%20his%20calm%2C%20was%20a%20member%20of%20the%20student%20branch%20of%20the%20Muslim%20Brotherhood%20at%20the%20Islamic%20University%20of%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20joined%20Hamas%20in%201987%2C%20when%20the%20group%20was%20founded%20as%20the%20first%20Palestinian%20intifada%2C%20or%20uprising%2C%20broke%20out%20against%20Israeli%20occupation%2C%20lasting%20until%201993.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20that%20time%2C%20Haniyeh%20was%20imprisoned%20by%20Israel%20several%20times%20and%20then%20expelled%20to%20south%20Lebanon%20for%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20footage%20broadcast%20by%20Hamas-linked%20media%20on%20Saturday%2C%20Haniyeh%20is%20seen%20watching%20images%20on%20television%20of%20the%20unfolding%20Hamas%20attack%20on%20Israel%20before%20joining%20other%20Hamas%20leaders%20in%20a%20prayer%20to%20%26quot%3Bthank%20Allah%20for%20this%20victory%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMohammed%20Deif%2C%20the%20'chief%20of%20staff'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Israel%20Hamas%20War%2C%20Mohammed%20Deif%3A%20%26quot%3BTwo%20Brains%2C%20One%20Mastermind%26quot%3B%3A%20How%20A%20Hamas%20Commander%20Planned%20Israel%20Attack%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fpulthnp_mohammed-deif_625x300_11_October_23.jpg%3Fdownsize%3D340%3A209%3Fdownsize%3D360%3A*%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20elusive%20Deif%2C%20who%20heads%20Hamas's%20armed%20wing%2C%20the%20Ezzdine%20al-Qassam%20Brigades%2C%20is%20Israel's%20public%20enemy%20number%20one%20and%20a%20man%20they%20tried%20to%20assassinate%20at%20least%20six%20times.%20He%20has%20been%20on%20the%20US%20list%20of%20%26quot%3Binternational%20terrorists%26quot%3B%20since%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EConsidered%20by%20Hamas%20a