%20Sam%20Kriegman%2C%20who%20led%20the%20work%2C%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20university's%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20told%20the%20AI%20that%20we%20wanted%20a%20robot%20that%20could%20walk%20across%20land.%20Then%20we%20simply%20pressed%20a%20button%20and%20presto!%20It%20generated%20a%20blueprint%20for%20a%20robot%20in%20the%20blink%20of%20an%20eye%20that%20looks%20nothing%20like%20any%20animal%20that%20has%20ever%20walked%20the%20earth.%20I%20call%20this%20process%20'instant%20evolution'%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20AI%20programme%20evaluated%20the%20design%2C%20found%20defects%2C%20and%20chipped%20away%20at%20the%20simulated%20block%20to%20alter%20its%20structure%20with%20each%20updated%20version.%20The%20virtual%20robot%20eventually%20developed%20the%20ability%20to%20bounce%2C%20hop%2C%20and%20shuffle.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20discovery%20is%20the%20first%20step%20towards%20research%20in%20quest%20to%20explore%20the%20potential%20of%20artificial%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20robot%20itself%20is%20unassuming%20-%20small%2C%20squishy%20and%20misshapen.%20And%2C%20for%20now%2C%20it%20is%20made%20of%20inorganic%20materials.%20But%20Mr%20Kriegman%20said%20it%20represents%20the%20first%20step%20in%20a%20new%20era%20of%20AI-designed%20tools%20that%2C%20like%20animals%2C%20can%20act%20directly%20on%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20people%20look%20at%20this%20robot%2C%20they%20might%20see%20a%20useless%20gadget%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20see%20the%20birth%20of%20a%20brand-new%20organism.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697175660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fac1j7bo8_ai-developed-robot-1200_625x300_13_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Finstant-evolution-new-ai-tool-can-design-robots-from-scratch-in-seconds-4477014%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20artificial%20intelligence%20programme%20created%20a%