eshow%2F104385868.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rohit%20and%20Virat's%20last%20match%20against%20Pakistan%20in%20an%20ICC%20event%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697164718000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104385597%2Cimgsize-172752.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fodi-world-cup-india-vs-pakistan-rohit-sharma-and-virat-kohlis-last-match-against-pakistan-in-an-icc-event%2Farticleshow%2F104385613.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rohit%20Sharma%20and%20Virat%20Kohli%20will%20face%20Pakistan%20in%20an%20ICC%20event%20for%20what%20could%20potentially%20be%20for%20the%20last%20time.%20The%20two%20Indian%20cricketers%20first%20played%20against%20Pakistan%20in%20a%20senior%20men's%20global%20event%20in%20South%20Africa%2C%20with%20Rohit%20starring%20in%20the%202007%20T20%20World%20Cup%20and%20Kohli%20in%20the%202009%20Champions%20Trophy.%20While%20Rohit%20had%20a%20successful%20start%2C%20Kohli%20used%20his%20early%20dismissal%20as%20a%20lesson%20and%20became%20one%20of%20the%20most%20efficient%20chasers%20in%20white-ball%20cricket.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22NITIN%20NAIK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fodi-world-cup-india-vs-pakistan-rohit-sharma-and-virat-kohlis-last-match-against-pakistan-in-an-icc-event%2Farticleshow%2F104385613.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CAG%3A%20After%20Verbal%20Orders%20to%20%E2%80%98Stop%20all%20Field%20Work%E2%80%99%2C%20Officers%20Ask%20for%20Written%20Orders%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F12153943%2FEe5Ey1CUwAMmwIG.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20the%20first%20week%20of%20October%2C%20there%20were%20%E2%80%9Cverbal%20orders%E2%80%9D%20passed%20in%20the%20Comptroller%20and%20Auditor%20General%20(CAG)%E2%80%99s%20office%20in%20New%20Delhi%20to%20%E2%80%9Cstop%20all%20field%20work%E2%80%9D.%20This%20field%20work%20is%20vital%20for%20the%20auditing%20of%20ministries%20and%20departments%20%E2%80%93%20that%20eventually%20results%20in%20reports%20put%20out%20by%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20official%20audit%20body%20and%20helps%20in%20establishing%20accountability%20and%20checks%20on%20government%20spending%20and%20finances.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20learnt%20that%20officers%20in%20the%20office%20have%20said%20they%20will%20pass%20down%20these%20instructions%20%E2%80%93%20to%20%E2%80%9Cstop%20all%20field%20work%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20to%20those%20in%20the%20field%20(comprising%20between%2030%25-40%25%20of%20the%20staff)%20only%20once%20they%20get%20written%20orders.%20Following%20purely%20verbal%20orders%20will%20leave%20them%20vulnerable%20to%20any%20inquiry%20or%20legal%20action%2C%20should%20this%20matter%20be%20opened%20by%20any%20future%20government%20or%20even%20the%20present%20one%20at%20a%20later%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20CAG%20Girish%20Chandra%20Murmu%20is%20said%20to%20be%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20signing%20any%20report%E2%80%9D%20that%20necessarily%20needs%20to%20bear%20his%20signature%2C%20along%20with%20that%20of%20the%20officer-in-charge%2C%20invariably%20an%20officer%20of%20the%20Indian%20Audit%20and%20Accounts%20Service%20(IA%26amp%3BAS).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWithout%20the%20signatures%20of%20the%20CAG%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.constitutionofindia.net%2Farticles%2Farticle-151-audit-reports%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DArticle%2520151%252C%2520Constitution%2520of%2520India%2Cbefore%2520each%2520House%2520of%2520Parliament.%5C%22%3Ethe%20reports%20cannot%20be%20placed%20in%20parliament%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMurmu%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fafter-resigning-as-jk-lg-g-c-murmu-appointed-as-new-cag%5C%22%3Eappointed%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%202020%20as%20the%20Comptroller%20and%20Auditor%20General%20of%20India.%20He%20is%20a%201985-batch%20Gujarat%20cadre%20Indian%20Administrative%20Service%20(IAS)%20officer%2C%20believed%20to%20be%20a%20trusted%20aide%20of%20both%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah.%20Prior%20to%20his%20appointment%20as%20the%20CAG%2C%20Murmu%20was%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmodi-shahs-trusted-aide-girish-chandra-murmu-appointed-lg-of-jk%5C%22%3Efirst%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0after%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%20and%20the%20downgrading%20of%20its%20status%20to%20a%20Union%20Territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20CAG%20is%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20topmost%20financial%20watchdog%2C%20constitutionally%20mandated%20to%20audit%20the%20finances%20of%20the%20Union%20and%20state%20governments%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20verbal%20orders%20which%20have%20created%20considerable%20turmoil%20in%20the%20CAG%E2%80%99s%20office%20come%20close%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fofficers-cag-reports-ayushman-bharat-bharatmala-transferred%5C%22%3Etransfers%20of%20three%20officers%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20on.%3C%2Fa%3E%20These%20officers%20were%20in%20charge%20of%20audit%20reports%20that%20exposed%20corruption%20in%20the%20Dwarka%20Expressway%20project%20and%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20%E2%80%93%20both%20launched%20by%20Modi%20with%20great%20fanfare.%20A%20third%20officer%20who%20had%20initiated%20the%20audit%20of%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20report%20was%20also%20transferred.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFollowing%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20report%2C%20opposition%20parties%20including%20the%20Congress%2C%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20and%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcag-officers-transfers-opposition-accuses-modi-government-intimidation%5C%22%3Eaccused%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20BJP%20government%20of%20%E2%80%9Ccorruption%E2%80%9D%20and%20intimidation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20CAG%E2%80%99s%20office%20for%20a%20comment.%20This%20report%20will%20be%20updated%20when%20a%20response%20is%20received.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20CAG%E2%80%99s%20office%20during%20the%20first%20tenure%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%20raised%20eyebrows%20for%20what%20appeared%20to%20be%20a%20markedly%20low%20level%20of%20activity.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fthesundaystandard%2F2021%2Fmar%2F07%2Fcaged-top-audit-bodys-reports-on-centres-money-management-down-by-75-per-cent-2273200.html%5C%22%3EAn%20RTI%20application%20filed%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20New%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0showed%20in%202021%2C%20that%20CAG%20reports%20relating%20to%20Union%20ministries%20and%20departments%20came%20down%20from%2055%20in%202015%20to%20merely%2014%20in%202020%20%E2%80%93%20a%20fall%20of%20nearly%2075%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECAG%20reports%2C%20once%20treated%20as%20a%20matter%20of%20governance-related%20tedium%2C%20gained%20political%20currency%20first%20in%20NDA-1%20when%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20was%20the%20prime%20minister.%20The%20then%20defence%20minister%2C%20George%20Fernandes%2C%20had%20to%20resign%20after%20%E2%80%98Coffin-gate%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20involved%20a%20CAG%20report%20on%20high%20expenses%20incurred%20in%20the%20purchase%20of%20caskets%20for%20Indian%20soldiers%20killed%20in%20action.%20Later%2C%20as%20Vinod%20Rai%20released%20audit%20reports%20on%20the%20Commonwealth%20Games%202010%2C%202G%20spectrum%20and%20coal%20policies%2C%20it%20led%20to%20a%20severe%20erosion%20of%20public%20faith%20in%20the%20UPA.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20monsoon%20session%20of%20Parliament%20saw%2012%20CAG%20reports%20being%20placed%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20house%2C%20severely%20castigating%20some%20Union%20government%20ministries%20and%20departments%2C%20and%20pointing%20to%