2%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6528644f55f52b01b35e7f5e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECaroline%20Ellison%20was%20widely%20considered%20the%20most%20important%20witness%20of%20the%20trial.%20But%20the%20defense%20line%20of%20questioning%20switched%20from%20topic%20to%20topic%20without%20a%20clear%20narrative.%3Cp%3EChelsea%20Jia%20Feng%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3ESam%20Bankman-Fried's%20defense%20attorneys%20have%20yet%20to%20demonstrate%20a%20clear%20strategy.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3ETheir%20cross%20of%20Caroline%20Ellison%2C%20arguably%20the%20biggest%20witness%20in%20the%20case%2C%20was%20noticeably%20repetitive.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EEllison's%20testimony%20got%20more%20interesting%20once%20the%20lead%20prosecution%20redirected%20questioning%20after%20the%20defense.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20been%20a%20bumpy%20start%20for%20disgraced%20crypto%20mogul%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fftx-crypto-king-sam-bankman-fried-rise-and-fall-2022-11%5C%22%3ESam%20Bankman-Fried%3C%2Fa%3E's%20defense%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEx-girlfriend%20and%20ex-Alameda-CEO%20Caroline%20Ellison%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-bankman-fried-sbf-fraud-trial-ftx-explainer-2023-10%5C%22%3Ereturned%20to%20the%20witness%20stand%20in%20Manhattan%20federal%20court%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Thursday%20for%20a%20cross-examination%20frequently%20interrupted%20with%20objections%20and%20sidebars.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAttorney%20Mark%20Cohen%2C%20representing%20Bankman-Fried%2C%20skipped%20from%20topic%20to%20topic%2C%20quizzing%20Ellison%20on%20various%20FTX%20accounts%2C%20his%20client's%20work%20personality%2C%20Ellison's%20balance%20sheets%20at%20Alameda%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcaroline-ellison-testify-criminal-trial-ftx-collapse-sam-bankman-fried-2023-9%5C%22%3Eand%20her%20cooperation%20agreement%20with%20the%20government.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEllison%2C%20clad%20in%20a%20plum%20purple%20dress%20and%20blazer%20for%20her%20third%20and%20final%20day%20of%20trial%20testimony%2C%20answered%20directly%20but%20wasn't%20afraid%20to%20let%20him%20know%20when%20she%20didn't%20recall%20a%20detail%20exactly%20as%20Cohen%20phrased%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEllison%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcaroline-ellison-freaked-out-alameda-owed-billions-lenders-2023-10%5C%22%3Ewidely%20been%20considered%20the%20most%20important%20witness%20of%20the%20trial%3C%2Fa%3E%20(unless%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-bankman-fried-sbf-fraud-trial-ftx-explainer-2023-10%5C%22%3EBankman-Fried%20decides%20to%20testify%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20his%20own%20behalf)%2C%20testified%20about%20how%2C%20in%20the%20summer%20of%202022%20as%20cryptocurrency%20prices%20were%20cratering%2C%20she%20felt%20trapped.%20She%20said%20she%20recognized%20that%20her%20nightmare%20scenario%20%E2%80%94%20where%20falling%20crypto%20prices%20would%20lead%20lenders%20to%20recall%20their%20loans%2C%20drastically%20increasing%20their%20exposure%20to%20disaster%20%E2%80%94%20had%20come%20to%20pass.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20around%20that%20time%2C%20Ellison%20said%2C%20she%20told%20Bankman-Fried%20she%20wanted%20to%20quit%20as%20the%20CEO%20of%20Alameda.%20She%20ultimately%20stayed%20at%20his%20urging%2C%20saying%20she%20didn't%20want%20Alameda%20and%20FTX%20to%20collapse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20his%20part%2C%20Cohen%20dipped%20into%20some%20personal%20topics%20but%20didn't%20get%20too%20deep%2C%20at%20one%20point%20mentioning%20another%20romantic%20relationship%20between%20Ellison%20and%20an%20employee%20at%20FTX%20and%20Alameda%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Ellison's%20lack%20of%20appetite%20for%20big%20risks%20compared%20to%20SBF.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20their%20on-again-off-again%20relationship%20definitively%20ended%20in%202022%2C%20Ellison%20said%20it%20was%20difficult%20to%20communicate%20with%20Bankman-Fried.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20CEO%20of%20FTX's%20sister%20company%20Alameda%20Research%2C%20Ellison%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%20seven%20financial%20fraud%20and%20conspiracy%20charges%20in%20December.%20She%20quickly%20agreed%20to%20work%20with%20prosecutors%2C%20landing%20a%20cooperation%20agreement%20that%20she%20hoped%20would%20result%20in%20a%20lesser%20sentence%2C%20according%20to%20her%20testimony.%20The%20maximum%20sentence%20for%20her%20seven%20charges%20total%20110%20years%20in%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20point%2C%20Cohen%20honed%20in%20on%20details%20from%20a%20November%202022%20FBI%20raid%20on%20Ellison's%20parent's%20home%2C%20where%20she%20was%20staying%20after%20returning%20from%20the%20Bahamas.%20In%20response%20to%20Cohen's%20questioning%2C%20Ellison%20admitted%20that%20she%20and%20her%20then-boyfriend%2C%20an%20unnamed%20individual%20who%20she%20said%20also%20worked%20at%20Alameda%20and%20FTX%2C%20were%20present%20at%20her%20parents'%20home%20during%20the%20raid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20dropping%20breadcrumbs%20about%20the%20mystery%20man%2C%20Cohen%20changed%20topics%20in%20his%20questioning.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20faced%20objections%20from%20the%20prosecution%2C%20who%20argued%20he%20was%20repeating%20facts%20established%20during%20their%20direct%20questioning.%20Judge%20Lewis%20Kaplan%20agreed%20at%20different%20points%20and%20reiterated%20his%20previous%20directives%20to%20move%20things%20along.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEllison's%20testimony%20sprang%20back%20to%20life%20when%20Cohen%20wrapped%20up%20and%20Assistant%20US%20Attorney%20Danielle%20Sassoon%20returned%20to%20the%20lectern%20to%20ask%20her%20more%20questions%2C%20prompting%20Ellison%20to%20explain%20how%20Bankman-Fried%20begged%20her%20not%20to%20quit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20told%20me%20I%20couldn't%2C%26quot%3B%20Ellison%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20too%20important%20to%20quit.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERea