aiming%20it%20was%20built%20on%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%E2%80%9D%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20two%20weeks%2C%20the%20police%20have%20arrested%20at%20least%2018%20persons%2C%20including%20some%20pastors%2C%20associated%20with%20the%20centre%2C%20under%20charges%20of%20attempt%20to%20murder%20and%20criminal%20conspiracy%2C%20for%20allegedly%20attacking%20the%20police%20and%20revenue%20officials%20when%20they%20had%20gone%20to%20survey%20the%20site%2C%20officials%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20prayer%20centre%20had%20been%20in%20the%20crosshairs%20of%20right-wing%20groups%20for%20several%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20demolition%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2011%2C%20bulldozers%20razed%20to%20the%20ground%20the%20two-storey%20building%20and%20boundary%20walls%20of%20the%20Jeevan%20Jyoti%20Satsang%20Prathna%20Kendra%2C%20in%20Bhulandih%20village%20in%20Jaunpur%2C%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20a%20team%20of%20revenue%20department%20officials%20and%20heavy%20police%20force%20from%20three%20police%20stations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDeputy%20superintendent%20of%20police%20(DSP)%20Gaurav%20Sharma%2C%20the%20circle%20officer%20of%20Kerakat%2C%20under%20which%20the%20said%20village%20is%20located%2C%20said%20that%20revenue%20officials%20from%20the%20tehsil%20removed%20the%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20encroachment%E2%80%9D%20with%20the%20support%20of%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20September%2C%20the%20local%20administration%20had%20lodged%20three%20first%20information%20reports%20(FIRs)%20against%20the%20managers%20of%20the%20prayer%20centre.%20One%20of%20the%20FIRs%20was%20filed%20on%20the%20complaint%20of%20a%20revenue%20official%2C%20who%20alleged%20that%20the%20campus%20of%20the%20prayer%20centre%20included%20land%20that%20had%20been%20%E2%80%9Cillegally%20occupied%E2%80%9D.%20The%20official%20claimed%20that%20it%20was%20originally%20a%20gram%20sabha%20land%2C%20allotted%20for%20a%20burial%20ground%20used%20by%20some%20Dalit%20communities%20(called%20a%20samadhi%20place)%2C%20as%20well%20as%20barren%20land%20tracts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDSP%20Sharma%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20demolished%20site%20measured%20around%2011%20biswa%2C%20which%20is%20equal%20to%20around%2015%2C000%20square%20feet%20or%200.14%20hectares.%20The%20officer%2C%20however%2C%20clarified%20that%20not%20all%20of%20the%20land%20was%20illegal.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20portion%20which%20was%20found%20to%20be%20legal%20and%20privately%20owned%20%E2%80%98was%20not%20touched%2C'%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20prayer%20centre%20had%20been%20operating%20from%20the%20past%2015%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20what%20prompted%20the%20police%20to%20launch%20an%20investigation%20about%20the%20centre%2C%20DSP%20Sharma%20said%20that%20they%20had%20received%20complaints%20on%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20online%20grievance%20registration%20portal%2C%20Integrated%20Grievance%20Registration%20and%20Monitoring%20System.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20prayer%20centre%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20for%20the%20prayer%20centre%20was%20conceived%20when%20Durga%20Prasad%20Yadav%20met%20Sebastian%20Martin%2C%20a%20self-proclaimed%20controversial%20divine%20healer%2C%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYadav%2C%20who%20was%20then%20a%20migrant%20belonging%20to%20a%20Hindu%20backward%20caste%20community%2C%20started%20personally%20attending%20Martin%E2%80%99s%20sessions%2C%20on%20the%20suggestion%20of%20a%20neighbour%E2%80%99s%20mother.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20contracted%20a%20chronic%20skin%20disease%20while%20working%20as%20an%20operator%20in%20a%20printing%20press%20in%20Bhopal.%20Desperate%20to%20heal%2C%20he%20travelled%20across%20the%20country%2C%20from%20Varanasi%20to%20Kolkata%2C%20and%20tried%20different%20kinds%20of%20treatments.%20He%20even%20spent%20a%20year%20in%20an%20ashram%2C%20surviving%20on%20boiled%20bael%20%5Ba%20plant%5D%20for%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThen%20he%20moved%20to%20Mumbai%20and%20started%20working%20as%20a%20security%20guard%20in%20a%20hotel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Mumbai%2C%20he%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20hydrocele.That%E2%80%99s%20when%20he%20started%20watching%20Martin%E2%80%99s%20healing%20sessions%20on%20television%2C%20and%20later%2C%20as%20mentioned%20earlier%2C%20even%20personally%20attended%20his%20sessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20family%20claimed%20he%20got%20miraculously%20cured%20in%20three%20weeks%2C%20though%20their%20claims%20were%20not%20verified%20or%20backed%20by%20any%20scientific%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFollowing%20that%2C%20he%20started%20his%20own%20prayer%20service%20and%20gradually%20relocated%20to%20his%20native%20village%2C%20Bhulandih.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Christmas%20in%202010%2C%20Yadav%2C%20now%20a%20pastor%2C%20started%20his%20first%20prayer%20service%2C%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98changai%20prathna%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20initially%20conducted%20the%20prayer%20service%20from%20his%20residence.%20Later%2C%20he%20built%20the%20prayer%20centre%20on%20his%20ancestral%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20compound%2C%20surrounded%20by%20lush%20fields%20away%20from%20the%20dense%20habitat%20of%20the%20village%2C%20bustled%20with%20visitors%20and%20devotees%20every%20Tuesday%20and%20Sunday.%20They%20came%20to%20listen%20to%20sermons%20on%20Jesus%20Christ%20and%20receive%20%E2%80%98divine%20healing%E2%80%99.%20People%20came%20from%20nearby%20villages%2C%20as%20well%20as%20neighbouring%20districts%20of%20Purvanchal%20%E2%80%93%20Azamgarh%2C%20Ghazipur%2C%20Mau%2C%20and%20Varanasi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20claimed%20that%20he%20could%20cure%20all%20kinds%20of%20illnesses%2C%20including%20cancer%2C%20tuberculosis%2C%20and%20epilepsy%2C%20through%20prayers%20and%20touch.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20house%20was%20decorated%20with%20photo%20frames%20of%20Jesus%20Christ%20and%20the%20cross%20%E2%80%93%20the%20most%20definite%20markers%20of%20Christianity.%20He%20believed%20in%20the%20ten%20commandments%20but%20insisted%20that%20they%20had%20not%20formally%20converted%20to%20Christianity%20and%20retained%20their%20Hindu%20OBC%20(Other%20Backward%20Class)%20identity%20and%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20bael%20tree%20and%20a%20tulsi%20plant%2C%20both%20considered%20auspicious%20by%20Hindus%2C%20were%20planted%20in%20the%20compound%20of%20his%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F12224108%2FPSX_20231012_203045.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22869%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F12224108%2FPSX_20231012_203045.jpg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F12224108%2FPSX_20231012_203045-300x169.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-679812%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22489%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20prayer%20centre%20in%20Bhulandih%20village%20in%20Jaunpur.%20Credit%3A%20Omar%20Rashid%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20assumed%20power%20in%20the%20state%2C%20the%20Christian%20prayer%20centre%20has%20been%20on%20the%20radar%20of%20local%20dominant%20caste%20and%20Hindutva%20groups.%20They%20have%20accused%20its%20managers%2C%20particularly%20chief%20pastor%20Yadav%2C%20of%20luring%20impoverished%20individuals%20to%20convert%20to%20Christianity%20and%20spreading%20misinformation%20about%20the%20Hindu%20religion.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20September%2C%20the%20United%20Christian%20Forum%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheleaflet.in%2Funited-christian-forum-details-the-worrying-increase-in-incidents-of-violence-against-christians-in-india%2F%5C%22%3Ehad%20identified%3C%2Fa%3E%20Jaunpur%20as%20among%20the%2013%20districts%20in%20India%20where%20%E2%80%9Cpractising%20Christianity%20is%20becoming%20dangerous%E2%80%9D.%20Jaunpur%20recorded%2013%20cases%20of%20violence%20against%20Christians%20%E2%80%93%20the%20fourth%20worst%20in%20the%20country%20this%20year%2C%20after%20Bastar%20and%20Kondagaon%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20and%20its%20neighbouring%20district%20of%20Azamgarh%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20according%20to%20the%20UCF.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETroubles%20brewed%20for%20the%20prayer%20centre%20since%20the%20BJP%20came%20to%20power%20in%20UP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20an%20FIR%20was%20lodged%20against%20Yadav%20and%20270%20others%2C%20including%20many%20of%20his%20associate%20pastors%2C%20based%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Ffir-lodged-on-court-order-for-promoting-conversion-to-christianity-cops%2Farticleshow%2F65710029.cms%5C%22%3Ecomplaint%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20a%20Hindu%20Jagran%20Manch%20activist.%20He%20alleged%20that%20Yadav%20tried%20to%20lure%20poor%20people%20to%20convert%20them%20to%20Christianity.%20The%20FIR%20was%20lodged%20on%20the%20orders%20of%20a%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBack%20then%2C%20UP%20did%20not%20have%20a%20law%20against%20unlawful%20conversion.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20booked%20under%20various%20penal%20offences%2C%20including%20giving%20dangerous%20drugs%20and%20other%20banned%20substances%20under%20the%20garb%20of%20medicine%2C%20cheating%2C%20defiling%20a%20place%20of%20worship%2C%20inducing%20people%20to%20believe%20they%20will%20attract%20divine%20displeasure%2C%20hurting%20by%20poison%2C%20and%20criminal%20conspiracy%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20administration%20barred%20prayers%20at%20the%20centre%2C%20Yadav%20evaded%20arrest%20and%20eventually%20got%20a%20stay%20in%20his%20favour%20from%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court.%20The%20organisers%20of%20the%20centre%20had%20also%20denied%20charges%20of%20forced%20conversion.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20September%2029%2C%20an%20FIR%20was%20lodged%20against%2012%20persons%2C%20including%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20brother%2C%20daughter%2C%20son%2C%20and%20nephew%2C%20and%2015-20%20other%20unknown%20persons%2C%20for%20allegedly%20pelting%20stones%20at%20and%20attacking%20the%20police%20force%20and%20revenue%20officials%20who%20had%20come%20to%20survey%20the%20land.%20The%20officials%20were%20allegedly%20hit%20with%20lathis%20and%20rods.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHussain%20Ahmad%2C%20naib%20tehsildar%2C%20a%20key%20officer%20in%20the%20revenue%20administration%2C%20in%20his%20complaint%20claimed%20that%20they%20%5Bthe%20pastor%20and%20his%20family%20and%20associates%5D%20wanted%20to%20teach%20the%20officials%20%E2%80%9Ca%20lesson%E2%80%9D%20for%20investigating%20the%20legality%20of%20the%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThree%20tehsil%20officials%20and%20four%20policemen%20got%20injured%20while%20an%20official%20SUV%20was%20damaged%20in%20the%20violence%2C%20alleged%20Ahmad.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20invokes%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20charges%2C%20including%20attempt%20to%20murder%2C%20criminal%20conspiracy%2C%20and%20rioting.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20October%201%2C%20another%20FIR%20was%20lodged%20against%20Yadav%20under%20Sections%203%20and%205%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Damage%20to%20Public%20Property%20Act%2C%201984%2C%20after%20a%20revenue%20team%20concluded%20that%20apart%20from%20having%20private%20land%2C%20the%20prayer%20centre%20had%20%E2%80%9Cillegally%E2%80%9D%20occupied%20the%20gram%20sabha%20and%20samadhi%20land%20and%20merged%20it%20into%20the%20compound.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20third%20FIR%20was%20lodged%20on%20the%20same%20day%20under%20Section%203%20(2)%20(va)%20of%20the%20stringent%20SC%2FST%20(Prevention%20of%20Atrocities)%20Act%2C%201989%2C%20on%20the%20complaint%20of%20a%20Dalit%20man%2C%20Dharamraj%2C%20who%20alleged%20that%20Yadav%20had%20%E2%80%9Cillegally%E2%80%9D%20transferred%20samadhi%20land%20to%20the%20prayer%20centre%2010%20to%2012%20years%20ago%2C%20through%20intimidation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYadav%2C%20his%20wife%20Leela%2C%20and%20brother%20Jai%20Prakash%20were%20named%20in%20the%20FIR%20and%20were%20accused%20of%20criminal%20conspiracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20October%209%2C%20police%20arrested%20Yadav%2C%20his%20wife%2C%20son%20Manish%2C%20and%20associates%2C%20pastor%20Sanjay%20Masih%20of%20Mirzapur%20and%20Manoj%20Jacob%2C%20UP%20president%20of%20the%20Christian%20forum%2C%20Rashtriya%20Isai%20Mahasangh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F12224208%2Fimage0.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22924%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F12224208%2Fimage0.png%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F12224208%2Fimage0-300x204.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-679813%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPolice%20after%20arresting%20pastor%20Durga%20Prasad%20Yadav%2C%20pastor%20Sanjay%20Masih%2C%20Manoj%20Jacob%20and%20Leela%20Yadav%20on%20October%209.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20Arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20also%20lodged%20a%20case%20against%20Yadav%20under%20the%20UP%20Prevention%20of%20Unlawful%20Conversion%20of%20Religion%20Act%2C%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESarvesh%20Singh%2C%20secretary%20of%20the%20caste%20outfit%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Kshatriya%20Mahasabha%20Yuva%2C%20who%20was%20leading%20the%20campaign%20against%20the%20prayer%20centre%2C%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20save%20my%20dharma.%20All%20those%20who%20were%20there%20at%20the%20centre%20were%20Hindus.%20Nobody%20was%20a%20Christian.%20There%20were%20attempts%20to%20convert%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESingh%20has%20filed%20several%20complaints%20against%20Yadav%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20people%20associated%20with%20the%20now-demolished%20centre%20are%20either%20in%20jail%20or%20absconding.%20Therefore%2C%20it%20was%20difficult%20to%20get%20their%20comments%20on%20the%20allegations%20levelled%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20source%20close%20to%20them%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity%2C%20that%20even%20if%20a%20portion%20of%20the%20centre%20included%20the%20gram%20sabha%20land%20due%20to%20the%20land%20consolidation%20reforms%20of%20the%20late%201970s%2C%20the%20administration%20could%20have%20exchanged%20it%20with%20the%20additional%20land%20owned%20by%20Yadav%20outside%20the%20compound.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20source%20said%20it%20was%20unfair%20on%20part%20of%20the%20administration%20to%20demolish%20a%20structure%20which%20existed%20for%20such%20a%20long%20time.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20many%20things%20illegal%20in%20these%20parts%20%5Bor%20areas%5D.%20Do%20they%20go%20and%20check%20the%20land%20registry%20of%20every%20temple%20and%20mosque%20to%20see%20if%20it%20was%20built%20on%20illegal%20land%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20administration%20removes%20the%20rubble%20from%20the%20site%2C%20Yadav%20and%20his%20associates%20are%20considering%20their%20next%20legal%20step.%20A%20district%20court%20is%20scheduled%20to%20hear%20their%20bail%20pleas%20next%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697133891000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F12223741%2FPSX_20231012_203134.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fup-christian-prayer-centre-demolished-in-jaunpur-claiming-it-was-built-on-illegal-land%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Over%20the%20last%20two%20weeks%2C%20police%20have%20arrested%20at%20least%2018%20persons%2C%20including%20some%20pastors%2C%20associated%20with%20the%20centre%2C%20under%20c