erg%20(%40finkd)%20citing%20the%20exhaustive%20investigations%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EWashington%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20Meta%20is%20culpable%20of%20abetting%20social%20disharmony%20and%20inciting%20communal%20hatred%20in%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ELetter%20by%20INDIA%20parties%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffacebook%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40Facebook%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98s%20Mr.%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffinkd%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40finkd%3C%2Fa%3E)%20citing%20the%20exhaustive%20investigations%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fwashingtonpost%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40washingtonpost%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Meta%20is%20culpable%20of%20abetting%20social%20disharmony%20and%20inciting%20communal%20hatred%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%5BLetter%20Below%5D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F2wnUa5xHbz%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F2wnUa5xHbz%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20(%40kharge)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkharge%2Fstatus%2F1712473551490761026%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2012%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EINDIA%20parties%20also%20write%20to%20Google%E2%80%99s%20Sundar%20Pichai%20on%20YouTube%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDeccanHerald%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40DeccanHerald%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F8XCWgblti8%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F8XCWgblti8%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Shemin%20(%40shemin_joy)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fshemin_joy%2Fstatus%2F1712485151585017898%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2012%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20letter%20to%20Zuckerberg%2C%20the%20opposition%20parties%20said%20that%20the%20India%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(INDIA)%20is%20an%20alliance%20of%2028%20political%20parties%20in%20India%20that%20represent%20the%20combined%20opposition%20coalition%20and%20are%20the%20ruling%20alliance%20in%2011%20states%20and%20represent%20nearly%20half%20of%20all%20Indian%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20may%20be%20aware%20of%20the%20recent%20exposes%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EWashington%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%20newspaper%20about%20the%20role%20of%20WhatsApp%20and%20Facebook%20in%20aiding%20the%20communal%20hatred%20campaign%20of%20the%20ruling%20BJP.%20Specifically%2C%20the%20article%20cites%20details%20of%20how%20this%20vile%2C%20communally%20divisive%20propaganda%20is%20carried%20out%20using%20WhatsApp%20groups%20by%20BJP%20members%20and%20supporters.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20another%20article%20titled%20%E2%80%98Under%20India%E2%80%99s%20pressure%2C%20Facebook%20let%20propaganda%20and%20hate%20speech%20thrive%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EPost%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20elucidated%20with%20evidence%20the%20blatant%20partisanship%20by%20Facebook%20India%20executives%20towards%20the%20ruling%20dispensation.%20This%20was%20well%20known%20to%20us%20in%20the%20Opposition%20for%20a%20long%20time%20and%20have%20even%20raised%20it%20several%20times%20in%20the%20past%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20very%20clear%20from%20these%20exhaustive%20investigations%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EWashington%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20Meta%20is%20culpable%20of%20abetting%20social%20disharmony%20and%20inciting%20communal%20hatred%20in%20India.%20Further%2C%20we%20have%20data%20that%20shows%20algorithmic%20moderation%20and%20suppression%20of%20Opposition%20leaders%E2%80%99%20content%20on%20your%20platform%20while%20also%20promoting%20ruling%20party%20content%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSuch%20blatant%20partisanship%20and%20bias%20towards%20one%20political%20formation%20by%20a%20private%20foreign%20company%20is%20tantamount%20to%20interfering%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20democracy%2C%20one%20that%20we%20in%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20will%20not%20take%20lightly%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20letter%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20light%20of%20the%20upcoming%20national%20elections%20in%202024%2C%20it%20is%20our%20earnest%20and%20urgent%20plea%20to%20you%20to%20consider%20these%20facts%20seriously%20and%20ensure%20immediately%20that%20Meta%E2%80%99s%20operations%20in%20India%20remain%20neutral%20and%20are%20not%20used%20wittingly%20or%20unwittingly%20to%20cause%20social%20unrest%20or%20distort%20India%E2%80%99s%20much%20cherished%20democratic%20ideals%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20was%20signed%20by%20AICC%20general%20secretary%20organisation%20K.C.%20Venugopal.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697133599000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F20152646%2FF1PwVKDXoAUTyA3.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Findia-bloc-writes-to-facebook-google-ceos-on-communal-hatred-neutrality%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20letters%20came%20after%20the%20'Washington%20Post'%20flagged%20alleged%20bias%20of%20Facebook%2C%20WhatsApp%2C%20and%20YouTube%20towards%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20and%20the%20Modi%20government.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Findia-bloc-writes-to-facebook-google-ceos-on-communal-hatred-neutrality%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amazon's%20expansion%20into%20logistics%20services%20could%20unlock%20%24100%20bn%20in%20revenue%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697133458000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F