%2Fus-arranging-evacuation-flights-for-americans-who-want-to-leave-israel-as-war-with-hamas-rages%2Famp_articleshow%2F104380259.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-arranging-evacuation-flights-for-americans-who-want-to-leave-israel-as-war-with-hamas-rages%2Famp_articleshow%2F104380259.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20Reminds%20Israel%20of%20Obligation%20to%20Observe%20Laws%20of%20War%2C%20Reiterates%20Support%20for%20Palestinian%20State%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2F14143039%2F2018_1-14-Benjamin-Netanyahu-and-Narendra-Modi26231292_10159929705395165_4506447465273333604_n.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20While%20Israel%20continues%20to%20pound%20Gaza%20amidst%20signs%20of%20an%20imminent%20invasion%2C%20India%20on%20Thursday%20(October%2012)%20noted%20that%20there%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cuniversal%20obligation%E2%80%9D%20to%20observe%20international%20humanitarian%20law%20and%20its%20reiterated%20support%20for%20a%20viable%20and%20independent%20Palestinian%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20additional%20nuance%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20stance%20was%20given%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20for%20the%20first%20time%20after%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20tweeted%20an%20initial%20response%20to%20the%20terror%20attack%20by%20Hamas%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMore%20than%201%2C200%20Israelis%20were%20killed%20when%20Hamas%20members%20breached%20the%20border%20with%20Israel%20from%20Gaza%20last%20Saturday.%20In%20retaliation%2C%20Israel%20air%20strikes%20have%20hit%20Gaza%20relentlessly%2C%20killing%20over%201%2C417%20people%20and%20rendering%20300%2C000%20people%20homeless.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%20had%20also%20conveyed%20the%20message%20of%20%E2%80%9Csolidarity%E2%80%9D%20with%20Israel%20in%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fmodi-reiterates-solidarity-phone-call-netanyahu-israel-hamas%5C%22%3EOctober%2010%20phone%20call%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%2C%20as%20well%20as%20condemned%20terrorism%20in%20all%20its%20forms%20and%20manifestations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20stance%20had%20till%20now%20seemed%20like%20an%20outlier%20in%20the%20reactions%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fhow-countries-across-the-world-reacted-to-hamas-attack-and-israel-palestine-war%5C%22%3Einternational%20community%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20expressed%20overwhelming%20sympathy%20for%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20suffering%2C%20but%20were%20also%20concerned%20about%20the%20scale%20of%20counter-attacks%20and%20called%20for%20the%20need%20to%20exercise%20maximum%20restraint.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETwo%20days%20later%2C%20the%20MEA%20spokesperson%20gave%20an%20additional%20context%20to%20the%20Indian%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20questions%20on%20whether%20Modi%20had%20told%20Netanyahu%20that%20this%20was%20%E2%80%98not%20an%20era%20for%20war%E2%80%99%20and%20voiced%20the%20need%20for%20restraint%2C%20MEA%20spokesperson%20Arindam%20Bagchi%20replied%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20do%20believe%20that%20there%20is%20a%20universal%20obligation%20to%20observe%20international%20humanitarian%20law.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20added%20that%20there%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cglobal%20responsibility%20to%20fight%20the%20menace%20of%20terrorism%20in%20all%20its%20forms%20and%20manifestations%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20echoed%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%98not%20an%20era%20for%20war%E2%80%99%20phrase%20was%20first%20mentioned%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20to%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20in%20September%202022.%20It%20was%20repeatedly%20highlighted%20as%20a%20sign%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20high-moral%20position%20on%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20and%20inserted%20into%20multilateral%20joint%20statements%20by%20Indian%20diplomats.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20had%20urged%20Israel%20to%20follow%20the%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjoe-biden-urges-israel-to-follow-rules-of-war-4473319%5C%22%3Erules%20of%20war%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D.%20The%20Israeli%20government%20had%20vowed%20for%20the%20complete%20destruction%20of%20Hamas%20and%20had%20cut%20of%20all%20electricity%2C%20water%2C%20and%20fuel%20links%20to%20Gaza.%20It%20was%20the%20first%20time%20that%20the%20US%2C%20which%20had%20sent%20arms%20to%20Israel%20and%20an%20aircraft%20carrier%20to%20the%20region%2C%20had%20asked%20Israel%20to%20exercise%20restraint.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20day%20earlier%2C%20EU%20foreign%20policy%20chief%20Josep%20Borrell%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2Fvideo%2F2023%2Foct%2F11%2Feu-israel-right-defend-decisions-contrary-international-law-josep-borrell-video%5C%22%3Ehad%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20while%20Israel%20had%20the%20%E2%80%9Cright%20to%20defend%20but%20it%20has%20to%20be%20done%20accordingly%20with%20international%20law%2C%20humanitarian%20law%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20answering%20another%20query%2C%20Bagchi%20said%20that%20there%20was%20no%20change%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20Palestine%20policy.%20%E2%80%9COur%20policy%20in%20this%20regard%20has%20been%20long-standing%20and%20consistent.%20India%20has%20always%20advocated%20the%20resumption%20of%20direct%20negotiations%20towards%20establishing%20a%20sovereign%2C%20independent%20and%20viable%20State%20of%20Palestine%20living%20within%20secure%20and%20recognised%20borders%2C%20side%20by%20side%20at%20peace%20with%20Israel.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20position%20on%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20became%20politicised%2C%20with%20the%20Modi%20government%20seen%20as%20having%20forged%20closer%20ties%20with%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20statement%20mentioned%20the%20need%20to%20stop%20the%20violence%20and%20referred%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Clegitimate%20aspirations%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20people.%20The%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janta%20Party%20had%20accused%20the%20Congress%20of%20playing%20%E2%80%9Cvote%20bank%20politics%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20first%20chartered%20flight%20with%20Indian%20nationals%20is%20expected%20to%20reach%20India%20on%20Friday%20morning%20(October%2013)%2C%20as%20per%20MEA.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EExternal%20affairs%20minister%20S.%20Jaishankar%20had%20announced%20%E2%80%98Operation%20Ajay%E2%80%99%20to%20bring%20back%20Indian%20nationals%20in%20Israel%20on%20Wednesday%20night%20(October%2011).%20He%20chaired%20a%20meeting%20of%20MEA%20officials%20in%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20Bhawan%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEAM%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDrSJaishankar%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40DrSJaishankar%3C%2Fa%3E%20chaired%20a%20meeting%20today%20to%20review%20preparations%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FOperationAjay%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23OperationAjay%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FTeamMEA%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23TeamMEA%3C%2Fa%3E%20stands%20ready%20to%20assist%20our%20citizens%20to%20return%20home.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FzK0iTKFjob%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FzK0iTKFjob%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Arindam%20Bagchi%20(%40MEAIndia)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMEAIndia%2Fstatus%2F1712385070152245458%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2012%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBagchi%20said%20that%20while%20the%20capacity%20of%20the%20chartered%20flight%20was%20240%20passengers%2C%20it%20was%20not%20certain%20if%20it%20will%20return%20on%20full%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20hoping%20(to%20have%20a%20full%20flight).%20How%20many%20people%20can%20get%20into%20that%20fli